{"tid":10904,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得個女神聯賽post好煩？","createTime":"2016-11-29T06:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T09:48:48.000Z","uid":269,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d570147a3105df68d0cf6115e3c5c35148c4fcf","tid":10904,"uid":269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:09:15.000Z","msg":"覺得：正評<br />\n唔覺：負評<br />\n<br />\n有上過膠登娛樂台就知我點解要開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲早實搞到成版都係聯賽post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3109449cd97100f1397ff91b5050504598d8f39e","tid":10904,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:20:24.000Z","msg":"今次我可以解答你<br />\n我就係有留意過對面既人當年搞呢個活動時既不足，不過個概念係有得諗，不過高登搞開女神選舉我就無意引入，難得今次有新平台新機會，點解唔試?上到報既話又加到網站知名度<br />\n所以今次個比賽會加以改良，唔會好似膠登班智障咁戇鳩開到成個版面都係post<br />\n大家都係想LIHKG好啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf80ebf75972878a66f453cf927ae09ba5d58a33","tid":10904,"uid":7426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:24:04.000Z","msg":"以為樓主老婆又要俾人拉上榜"},{"pid":"6c783f669f12da503ddd7531f4b364142bc75ccd","tid":10904,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:26:04.000Z","msg":"絕對明白某啲人既憂慮架<br />\n膠登當年 每輪開41個post，實屬離譜<br />\n我地LIHKG香港女神聯賽最多每輪只有數個<br />\n所有比賽會集合一齊以回覆方式比大家玩，詳情遲啲過左提名期同資格賽階段就會公佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f87bdffe654f7f8cbf69c39d1fed91c9c8cae5","tid":10904,"uid":269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:02:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為樓主老婆又要俾人拉上榜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb916f92a4287ca483f0c813a21908036e51797","tid":10904,"uid":269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite